<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr />

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 250, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-stripped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Fam tattooed actually, selfies affogato snackwave heirloom chicharrones waistcoat. Brunch keytar drinking vinegar distillery hashtag YOLO. Tacos blog vegan shaman live-edge food truck 90's, la croix banjo. Neutra knausgaard four loko vexillologist salvia tacos kickstarter brunch. Lumbersexual yuccie health goth, master cleanse keffiyeh typewriter godard forage brooklyn helvetica coloring book chillwave locavore fingerstache ennui. Salvia venmo master cleanse wayfarers, subway tile umami pug kinfolk.i</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controlers="jobHistory"
          >
            JobHistory
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controlers="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#courses"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controlers="courses"
          >
            Courses
          </button>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              job 1
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="courses">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Course 1
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              Course 2
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              Course 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>